<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="with-effects" style="background:#131313;opacity:1;color:#5f5">
<head>

    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1,minimum-scale=1,maximum-scale=1,user-scalable=no">
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/img/favicon.webp" />
    <meta name="theme-color" content="black">
    <title>The Long Journey | FOnline Roleplay</title>
    <meta name="description" content="FOnline Roleplaying Community Project">
    <meta name="keywords" content="fonline,roleplay,rpg,online,heavy rp,heavy roleplay,immersion,mod">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/normalize/8.0.1/normalize.min.css" type="text/css" />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Share+Tech+Mono" rel="stylesheet">

    <script>var exports = {};</script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@splidejs/splide@3.5.0/dist/js/splide.cjs.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@splidejs/splide@3.5.0/dist/css/splide.min.css" type="text/css"/>
    <script>
        document.addEventListener('DOMContentLoaded', function(){
            let splide = new Splide('#features');
            splide.mount();
        });
    </script>

    <style>
        * {
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }
        html, body {
            padding: 0;
            margin: 0;
            font-family: 'Share Tech Mono';
        }
        .features {
            margin: 0 auto;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            max-width: 1024px;
        }
        .features > div {
            width: 100%;
            margin-bottom: .3%;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: row;
        }
        .features > div > div {
            border: 1px solid green;
            width: 100%;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
        }
        .features > div:nth-child(even) {
            flex-direction: row-reverse;
        }
        .features-item-title {
            max-width: 20%;
        }
        #features .splide__slide {
            border: 1px solid green;
            padding: 1rem 5rem;
            height: 400px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    {# <section style="background: url(img/background.jpg) center/cover; height: 60vh">
        <img src="img/logo_lossy.webp">
        <div style="display: none">
            <p><strong>FOnline: The Long Journey</strong> is a Fаllоut 1/2 based online RPG, set in Fallout atmosphere, following the original parts canon and ideas.</p>

            <p>The game focuses on roleplay and survival, replicating the absolute ruthlessness of the Wastelands and the anarchic post nuclear world.</p>

            <p>Forget about being a "Chosen One" or some kind of superhuman being able to change the world around. Here you are nothing
                and nobody with the price of broken penny for the head of yours.</p>

            <p>Your character is fragile, your aim is to survive and thrive, your dream is to find your place in the unforgiving world.
                The place you have to fight for and the biggest enemy won't be the mutated fauna or the desert, but the very people around you.</p>
        </div>
    </section>#}
    <section>
        <div id="features" class="splide">
            <div class="splide__track">
                <ul class="splide__list">
                    {% for feature in sections.features %}
                    <li class="splide__slide" data-splide-interval="4" style="background: url({{ feature.image }}) center/cover">
                        <div class="features__info">
                            <div class="features__title">{{ feature.title }}</div>
                            <div class="features__description">{{ feature.description }}</div>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                    {% endfor %}
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</body>
</html>

